## Content Pipeline Stages (Blog_Post / LinkedIn_Post)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Tavily
    participant Agent as Blog/LinkedIn Agent
    participant ImgPrompt as Image Prompt Agent
    participant ImgGen as gpt-image-1
    participant Drive
    participant Sheets
    participant Telegram
    
    Orchestrator->>Blog_Trigger: {topic, audience, chatID}
    Blog_Trigger->>Tavily: Search(topic)
    Tavily-->>Blog_Trigger: Research Results
    Blog_Trigger->>Agent: Topic + Research + Audience
    Agent-->>Blog_Trigger: Written Content
    Agent->>ImgPrompt: Content → Visual Prompt
    ImgPrompt-->>Agent: Image Prompt
    Agent->>ImgGen: Generate Image
    ImgGen-->>Agent: Base64 Image
    Agent->>Drive: Upload PNG
    Drive-->>Agent: File Link
    Agent->>Sheets: Log {topic, audience, content, image, link}
    Agent->>Telegram: Send Content + Photo
    Telegram-->>User: Delivered
```

