## Governance & Audit Trail (Every Pipeline)

| Logged Field | Source | Purpose |
|--------------|--------|---------|
| **Request** | Trigger input | What was asked |
| **ID** | Drive file ID | Asset traceability |
| **Link** | Drive webViewLink | Direct asset access |
| **Post** | Agent output | Full content for review |
| **Title** | Image prompt title | Visual asset identifier |
| **Type** | "Post" / "Image" | Filter/segment |
| **Timestamp** | `{{ $now }}` | Temporal ordering |

