## Scaling Content Operations

| Dimension | Current | Scaling Path |
|-----------|---------|--------------|
| **Topics/Week** | ~10-20 | Batch Tavily calls, parallel agent execution |
| **Channels** | 4 (Blog, LI, Newsletter, IG) | Add X, Threads, TikTok via new tool workflows |
| **Languages** | EN only | Add `language` param → multilingual prompts |
| **Review** | Automated (Evaluator-Optimizer available) | Human-in-loop via HITL nodes |
| **Analytics** | Sheets logs | Connect to GA/BigQuery for ROI tracking |